data.description: NO HOA Country Living 2-Story 4 bedroom 3 bath Pool home has so many great features you won't want to miss! All bedrooms are up. Includes a big front porch with a stunning view of the greenbelt! Inside you will find a large kitchen with tray ceilings, dining area, a big utility room, an additional office and 2 living areas. Extended driveway, over-sized garage, wrought iron gates PLUS large 8 X 10 shed with loft, large 16 X 16 permitted shop with 2 lofts and lean to! Big backyard also features a swimming pool, beautiful flower beds, congregate decking and a back porch! Home is close to the lake, parks, schools and freeways! Recent updates include Brand New Black Roof, Matching Gutters, new up-to code water heaters up and down stairs! Pool just resurfaced with new pumps, sidewalk painted, Fireplace fixed and swept, HVAC serviced and new faucets installed. As Is, inside is ready for personal touches! Includes continued Home Warranty & Pool Table is negotiable! Schedule a Showing TODAY!
